uses-new-purge-thriller-1257483|archive-date=2020-05-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/the-purge-5-adds-will-patton-cassidy-freeman|title=The Purge 5 Adds Will Patton & Cassidy Freeman|last=Sprague|first=Mike|work=[[JoBlo.com|JoBlo.com]]|date=2019-11-23|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703211359/https://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/the-purge-5-adds-will-patton-cassidy-freeman|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年1月，據報導{{le|利文·藍賓|Leven Rambin}}加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/purge-5-leven-rambin-cast-blumhouse-universal-1202823640/|title='Purge 5': 'True Detective' Actress Leven Rambin Joins Universal-Blumhouse-Platinum Dunes Sequel|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2020-01-07|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417084022/https://deadline.com/2020/01/purge-5-leven-rambin-cast-blumhouse-universal-1202823640/|archive-date=2020-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
2019年7月，宣佈電影將在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]進行拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sherlock-holmes-3-10-new-films-shoot-california-1227463|title='Sherlock Holmes 3' Among 10 New Films to Shoot in California|last=Sandberg|first=Bryn Elise|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2019-07-29|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012190409/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sherlock-holmes-3-10-new-films-shoot-california-1227463|archive-date=2019-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並獲得了{{le|加利福尼亞電影委員會|California Film Commission}}近650萬美元的稅收抵免，為該系列中繼《[[國定殺戮日：無法無天|國定殺戮日：無法無天]]》後第二部獲得加利福尼亞稅收抵免的電影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/robert-downey-jr-sherlock-holmes-3-tax-credits-california-film-commission-purge-5-warner-bros-1202656129/|title='Sherlock Holmes 3' & 'Purge 5' Among 10 Features Bestowed Big Bucks From California Tax Credits|last=Patten|first=Dominic|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2019-07-29|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202131726/https://deadline.com/2019/07/robert-downey-jr-sherlock-holmes-3-tax-credits-california-film-commission-purge-5-warner-bros-1202656129/|archive-date=2019-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。製作定於2019年11月開始<ref name="THR1"/><ref name="screenrant"/>，並在[[聖地牙哥郡|聖地牙哥郡]]進行25天的拍攝<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://film.ca.gov/wp-content/uploads/LOCATION-CALIFORNIA-2020-PAGE-TURNER.pdf|title=Location California 2020|author=[[California_Film_Commission|California Film Commission]]|publisher=Boutique Editions|location=[[London|London]], England, UK|page=39|date=|access-date=2020-07-09|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223040146/https://film.ca.gov/wp-content/uploads/LOCATION-CALIFORNIA-2020-PAGE-TURNER.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/california-film-commissioner-colleen-bell-beyond-hollywood/|title=California's New Film Commissioner Colleen Bell Looks Beyond Hollywood|last=Williams|first=Trey|work=[[TheWrap|WrapPRO]]|date=2019-08-09|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200429014746/https://www.thewrap.com/california-film-commissioner-colleen-bell-beyond-hollywood/|archive-date=2020-04-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月10日至11日在[[波莫納_(加利福尼亞州)|波莫納]]進行拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailybulletin.com/2019/11/14/hot-dog-chicago-style-food-is-here-but-may-require-long-drive-frankly/|title=Hot dog! Chicago-style food is here but may require long drive, frankly|last=Allen|first=David|work=[[Inland_Valley_Daily_Bulletin|Inland Valley Daily Bulletin]]|date=2019-11-14|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115133641/https://www.dailybulletin.com/2019/11/14/hot-dog-chicago-style-food-is-here-but-may-require-long-drive-frankly/|archive-date=2019-11-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拍攝工作於2020年2月[[殺青|殺青]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2496135/the-purge-5-quick-things-we-know-about-the-forever-purge|title=The Purge 5: 8 Quick Things We Know About The Forever Purge|last=Eisenberg|first=Eric|work=CinemaBlend|date=2020-05-14|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529235747/https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2496135/the-purge-5-quick-things-we-know-about-the-forever-purge|archive-date=2020-05-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
