7|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927205748/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/blumhouses-forever-purge-halloween-kills-delay-release-2021-1302434/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本片因“强烈的暴力血腥场面且充斥不雅语言”被[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]評為「[[美国电影分级制度#美國電影協會電影分級|R級]]」<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Forever Purge Officially Rated R For Strong/Bloody Violence |url=https://screenrant.com/purge-5-movie-rated-r-violence-details/ |last=Pruner |first=Aaron |date=2021-03-31 |access-date=2021-05-13 |website=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]] |archive-date=2021-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513133656/https://screenrant.com/purge-5-movie-rated-r-violence-details/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

